'''Silas Lwakabamba''' (wavutse 1947) ni umwarimu [[Rwanda|w’umunyarwanda]] ukomoka muri [[Tanzaniya]] wabaye Minisitiri w’uburezi mu Rwanda kuva muri Nyakanga 2014 kugeza ku ya 24 Kamena 2015. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20130620151023/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=15281</ref> <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20120725074916/http://www.ku.ac.ke/schools/graduate/images/stories/docs/presentation/mapping.pdf</ref>

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Silas Lwakabamba yavukiye kandi yiga muri [[Tanzaniya]] . Yagiye muri kaminuza ya Leeds mu Bwongereza aho yize ibijyanye n’ubuhanga, arangiza BSc mu 1971 na PhD muri 1975. Nyuma yaje gusubira muri Tanzaniya aho yinjiye mu bakozi b'ishami ry'ubwubatsi muri kaminuza ya Dar es Salaam . Yabonye ubushobozi bwo kuba professor muri 1981, nyuma aba Umuyobozi w'ishami. Muri 1997, Silas Lwakabamba yabaye Umuyobozi washinze ikigo cy’ubumenyi n’ikoranabuhanga cya Kigali mu Rwanda (KIST) [[Rwanda|,]] naho mu 2006, agirwa umuyobozi wa [[kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda]], ikigo cya Leta kinini mu mashuri makuru mu gihugu. Yakomeje kuri uyu mwanya kugeza igihe yagenwe muri Gashyantare 2013 nka Minisitiri w’ibikorwa Remezo muri Guverinoma ya Rwanda<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20130620151023/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=15281</ref>

